    "@type" : "JobPosting",
    "title" : "Full-Time AI Engineer for Long-Term Role in Self-Funded Company",
    "description" : "<p>I'm the founder of a successful, self-funded company that's already automated several key business components, with plans to expand those automations further. In parallel, I'm building a SaaS product with a team of 8 full-stack developers (including a CTO) and a dedicated design team. We're AI-first, shipping features rapidly and iterating on user feedback to drive real revenue.</p><p>We're seeking an AI engineer who's extremely passionate about the field – someone who geeks out over emerging models, agents, and architectures – to join full-time and exclusively on our projects. This is a long-term commitment where you'll report directly to me and focus on automations for my core business, standalone AI products, micro-SaaS tools, and enterprise-level solutions. No side gigs; we're building a dedicated role with potential to help manage the SaaS company as it evolves (including opportunities to step in as we refresh parts of the team).</p><p><strong>What You'll Do:</strong></p><ul><li>Develop and deploy AI-driven features from concept to production, with a focus on both backend AI logic and front-end integrations.</li><li>Tackle challenges in areas like model fine-tuning, agent workflows, scalable integrations, and user-facing interfaces.</li><li>Contribute to roadmaps, experiment with cutting-edge tech, and help shape monetization strategies like tiered subscriptions.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>3+ years in AI engineering (Python, PyTorch/TensorFlow, LLMs, agents).</li><li>Experience shipping AI products in a team environment; strong front-end development skills, including UI/UX design capabilities.</li><li>US-based preferred for optimal time zone overlap (I'm based in Dubai but currently in Miami for the next 60 days).</li><li>Remote OK. Competitive package: $140k-$200k base, full benefits, flexible PTO.</li><li>Bonus: Familiarity with tools like LangChain, RAG, or domain-specific AI applications.</li></ul><p>If you're committed and excited to build impactful AI, send your resume, GitHub/portfolio, and a note on why this role appeals to you to <a href="mailto:jobs@yourcompany.com">the form linked below. </a>Be prepared for a Google Meet interview where we'll discuss your experience and fit. Serious inquiries only; no agencies or freelancers.</p>",
